<br>
<br>
<br>
<div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Real
Estate and the Capital Gains
Debate</span><br>
by Michael Hudson* and Kris Feder*<br>
Working Paper No. 187<br>
March 1997<br>
<br>
<small>*Research Associates, <br>
The Jerome Levy Economics Institute of Bard
College</small><br>
</div>
<div style="text-align: center;"></div>
1 <a href="#I._Introduction">Introduction</a><br>
2 <a href="#2._Depreciation_and_Capital_Gains">Depreciation and
Capital Gains</a><br>
