Converts Rent into Interest</a><br>
4 <a href="#4._Capital_Gains_Taxation_in_Real_Estate">Capital Gains
Taxation in Real Estate</a><br>
5 <a href="#5._Government_Statistics_on_Real_Estate">Government
Statistics on Real Estate Asset Gains</a><br>
6 <a href="#6._The_Political_Context_of_Real_Estate">The Political
Context of Real Estate Taxation</a><br>
7 <a href="#7._Policy_Conclusions">Policy Conclusions</a><br>
<br>
